com.intechcore.scomponents.scell.api

Interface IScellApiResolver


  • public interface IScellApiResolver
    The container of the SCell Public API dependencies

    Aimed to resolve or replace the required instances of the API

    Can be obtained by the following call: ScellApiEntryPoint.getApiResolverAsync()

    • Method Detail

      • resolve

        <TInstance> TInstance resolve(Class<TInstance> interfaceClass)
        Resolves a new instance or a singleton instance of the given interface. The type of the returned instance depends on the type that was chosen during the registration of the given interface.
        Type Parameters:
        TInstance - the type of the interface;
        Parameters:
        interfaceClass - the Class<TInstance> interface to be resolved;
        Returns:
        the corresponding instance.
        See Also:
        registerInstance(Class, Object), registerImplementation(Class, Class)

      • registerInstance

        <TInstance> void registerInstance(Class<TInstance> interfaceClass,
                                  TInstance instance)
        Binds an instance of the class to the given interface.

        The resolve(Class) method will always return an instance of the class of the given interface.

        Type Parameters:
        TInstance - the type of the interface.
        Parameters:
        interfaceClass - the interface to be bound;
        instance - an instance of the class to be bound;

      • registerImplementation

        <TInstance> void registerImplementation(Class<TInstance> interfaceClass,
                                        Class<? extends TInstance> implementation)
        Binds the given class to the given interface.

        The resolve(Class) method will always return the new instance of the given class bound to the given interface.

        Type Parameters:
        TInstance - type of the interface.
        Parameters:
        interfaceClass - interface to be bound;
        implementation - class to be bound;
